{
  "texts": [
    "Intrinsic issues are inseparable from how the technology itself works.",
    "Extrinsic issues are those emerging from a technology's deployment and use in different contexts, including those raised by the resulting relationship between humans and the relevant technology, such technology's impacts on society and the legitimacy of its intended goals.",
    "We propose that the practical issues arising from biologically inspired AI, including brain-inspired AI, can be organized in terms of (at least) the following main levels:",
    "• Operational, related to how AI works;",
    "• Instrumental, related to how people use AI;"
  ]
}